prosody-stt (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Core features:
    - Double-tap Ctrl to start/stop recording
    - Double-tap Escape to cancel recording
    - Visual waveform indicator
    - Automatic transcription using Whisper
    - Background operation with minimal UI
  * Debian package for easy installation

 -- Prosody Contributors <prosody@example.com>  Thu, 28 Jul 2024 12:00:00 +0000